<h3 id="initial-findings">Initial Findings</h3>

<p>Soundcloud is not very customizable. A few links below detail what is available.</p>

<h3 id="soundcloud-options">Soundcloud Options</h3>

<p><a href="https://pdfobject.com">PDFObject</a> - An open-source standards-friendly JavaScript utility for embedding PDF files into HTML documents. Recommends using PDFJS for full browser support.</p>

<p>Stack Overflow Post About <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/35286303/pdf-file-to-be-displayed-on-the-dialog-modal-via-bootstrap">Displaying a PDF in a Modal</a>. Uses <a href="https://pdfobject.com">PDFObject</a></p>

<p><a href="https://mozilla.github.io/pdf.js/">PDFJS</a> - by Mozilla. <a href="https://github.com/mozilla/pdf.js/wiki/Frequently-Asked-Questions#faq-support">Browser support listed here</a>.</p>

<p>Hereâ€™s a blog post highlighting all of the ways to <a href="http://jsgyan.blogspot.com/2017/12/how-to-display-pdf-in-html-web-page.html">Display a PDF in a Web Page</a>. The recommended method to address all browsers? <a href="https://mozilla.github.io/pdf.js/">PDFJS</a></p>

<p>An additional resource about <a href="http://hbekkouche.github.io/PDF.js-viewer-Example/">Using PDFJS In A Bootstrap Modal</a> - <a href="https://github.com/hbekkouche/PDF.js-viewer-Example/blob/master/index.html">Hereâ€™s the Markup</a></p>
